<i>adverb</i>: 굽실굽실 [굽씰굽씰], 굽실 [굽씰], 굽신굽신 [굽씬굽씬] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>굽실굽실 [굽씰굽씰]</dt><br>
<dd>1. with one's head down; with a deep bow</dd><br>
<dd>윗사람을 대하면서 허리나 고개를 자꾸 구부렸다 펴는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of continuing to bow one's head before a superior person.</dd><br>
<dd>2. in a servile manner; obsequiously; subserviently</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 잘 보이기 위해 자꾸 비굴하게 구는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>With the attitude of groveling subserviently to someone to win his/her favor.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>굽실 [굽씰]</dt><br>
<dd>1. with one's head down; with a deep bow</dd><br>
<dd>윗사람을 대하면서 허리나 고개를 구부렸다 펴는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of continuously bowing one's head before a superior person.</dd><br>
<dd>2. in a servile manner; obsequiously; subserviently</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 잘 보이기 위해 비굴하게 구는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>With the attitude of crawling to someone.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>굽신굽신 [굽씬굽씬]</dt><br>
<dd>1. with one's head down; with a deep bow</dd><br>
<dd>윗사람을 대하면서 허리나 고개를 자꾸 구부렸다 펴는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of continuing to bow one's head before a superior person.</dd><br>
<dd>2. in a servile manner; obsequiously; subserviently</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 잘 보이기 위해 자꾸 비굴하게 구는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>With the attitude of groveling subserviently to someone to win his/her favor.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>